      <div class="logo-text">
        <h1>BCS Lite</h1>
        <p>Bhāva Cognitive Screen · Enhanced Edition</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="section-title">Assessment Overview</div>
      <p style="font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.6;color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:18px;">
        This tool measures 5 cognitive domains in approximately 12–15 minutes. Ensure you are in a quiet environment before starting.
      </p>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px;">
